articles.title: Concussion Lawsuit Against Pop Warner Is Dismissed
articles.description: Two mothers blamed the youth football organization for the deaths of their sons, who were found to have a degenerative brain disease after a fatal motorcycle crash and suicide.
articles.content:
A federal court judge has dismissed a lawsuit against Pop Warner, saying the two women who sued the youth football organization failed to prove that their sons deaths were directly linked to head trauma sustained a decade earlier as young players.
